% Family domain
Socrates is a man.
Every man is mortal.
X is mortal if X is a man.

% Parent/ancestor
John is a person.
Mary is a person.
John is a parent of Mary.
X is an ancestor of Y if X is a parent of Y.
X is an ancestor of Y if X is a parent of Z and Z is an ancestor of Y.

% Users/roles
Leslie is a user.
Leslie has role admin.
X is an admin_user if X is a user and X has role admin.

% Negation
X can log in if X is a user and X is not banned.
